(184, 0, '第51节', '改变观念，改写人生', 'UploadFiles/vedio/20171023/vedio_1601508747066.mp3', '25:26', 1526, '海海老师', 0.00, NULL, '<p>Haw hadn''t found any Cheese yet, but as he ran through the Maze, he thought about what he had already learned.&nbsp;</p><p>Haw now realized that his new beliefs were encouraging new behaviors. He was behaving differently than when he kept returning to the same cheeseless station.&nbsp;</p><p>He knew that when you change what you believe, you change what you do.&nbsp;</p><p>You can believe that a change will harm you and resist it. Or you can believe that finding New Cheese will help you and embrace the change.&nbsp;</p><p>It all depends on what you choose to believe.&nbsp;</p><p>He wrote on the wall:</p><p>When You See That You Can Find And Enjoy New Cheese, You Change Course.&nbsp;</p><p><br /></p><p>单词&amp;短语</p><p>harm &nbsp; /hɑ:m/ &nbsp; v. 伤害</p><p>resist &nbsp; /rɪˈzɪst/ &nbsp; &nbsp;v. 抵抗，抗拒</p><p>embrace &nbsp; /ɪmˈbreɪs/ &nbsp; &nbsp; v. 拥抱</p><p>depend on sb./sth. &nbsp; 依靠，依赖，取决于</p><p>course &nbsp; /kɔ:s/ &nbsp; n. 过程，进程</p><p><br /></p>', 1508738423, 152, 152, 0, 0, 0, 1, 2, '', ''),
(185, 0, 'Live above them', '他障易除，心障难除', 'UploadFiles/vedio/20171026/vedio_8851509027735.mp3', '6:42', 402, '海海老师', 0.00, 'UploadFiles/product/20171026/1509027735434871.jpg', '<p>We never lose our demons. We only learn to live above them.&nbsp;</p><p>—&nbsp;电影 Doctor Strange 中，古一大师对 Mordo 说的话（音频中说成了对 Doctor Strange 说的话）<br /></p><p><br /></p><p><br /></p><p>他障易除，心障难除。</p><p>— 《鬼谷子的局》中，鬼谷子对苏秦说的话<br /></p>', 1509027735, 80, 80, 0, 0, 0, 3, 2, '', ''),
(186, 0, 'No one ever is. ', '我们无法左右时间', 'UploadFiles/vedio/20171029/vedio_6831509263087.mp3', '10:45', 645, '海海老师', 0.00, 'UploadFiles/product/20171029/1509263167775356.jpeg', '<p>1- Study and practice. Years of it. &nbsp;学习加练习，年复一年。</p><p>2- D.S.: I''m not ready. &nbsp; A.O.: No one ever is. We don''t get to choose our time. &nbsp;没人准备好。我们无法左右时间。</p><p>3- Death is what gives life meaning, to know your days are numbered, your time is short. 死亡赋予生命意义，让你知道你的日子屈指可数，你的时间是短暂的。</p>', 1509263087, 79, 79, 0, 0, 0, 3, 2, '', ''),
(187, 0, '第52节', '注意到小，就能把握好大', 'UploadFiles/vedio/20171029/vedio_4631509264735.mp3', '28:47', 1727, '海海老师', 0.00, NULL, '<p>Haw knew he would be in better shape now if he had dealt with the change much sooner and left Cheese Station C earlier. He would feel stronger in body and spirit and he could have coped better with the challenge of finding New Cheese. In fact, he probably would have found it by now if he had expected change, rather than wasting time denying that the change had already taken place.&nbsp;</p><p>He used his imagination again and saw himself finding and savoring New Cheese. He decided to proceed into the more unknown parts of the Maze, and found little bits of Cheese here and there. Haw began to regain his strength and confidence.&nbsp;</p><p>As he thought back on where he had come from, Haw was glad he had written on the wall in many places. He trusted that it would serve as a marked trail for Hem to follow through the Maze, if he ever chose to leave Cheese Station C.&nbsp;</p><p>Haw just hoped he was heading in the right direction. He thought about the possibility that Hem would read The Handwriting On The Wall and find his way.&nbsp;</p><p>He wrote on the wall what he had been thinking about for some time:</p><p>Noticing Small Changes Early Helps You Adapt To The Bigger Changes That Are To Come.&nbsp;</p><p><br /></p>', 1509264736, 153, 153, 0, 0, 0, 1, 2, '', ''),
