(12, 0, 530, 'Nowhere do 1980 census statistics dramatize more the American search for spacious living than in the Far West. \n请教老师这个句子的语法结构. \n因强调地域，是否将nowhere than in the far west放在一起更好呢? Thanks.', 1504098992, 0, 0, 1),
(13, 0, 21, 'Never before in American history has living alone been the predominant lifestyle. 是倒装句吗？还原过来是怎么样的？', 1504142154, 0, 0, 1),
